data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the sought-after Deer Hollow community of Pine Ridge, nestled in the serene East Lake Corridor. This remarkable 2BR/2BA second-floor condo is your gateway to luxurious and low-maintenance living. New A/C and water heater recently added. Prepare to be captivated by its open floor plan and private screened balcony that offers breathtaking views of conservation and the pristine natural surroundings. Step inside this meticulously designed condo, where every inch has been thoughtfully planned to maximize your comfort and space. The open-concept floor plan seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating an inviting atmosphere for both daily living and entertaining. The generously sized bedrooms offer ample space for relaxation and privacy, making it perfect for families, couples, or those who desire a guest room/home office setup. Wake up to the soothing sounds of nature right outside your window, and bask in the beauty of wildlife that graces your pond view on a daily basis. As a resident of Pine Ridge at Lake Tarpon Village, you'll experience a lifestyle reminiscent of a perpetual vacation. Take a refreshing dip in the lakefront heated pool, perfect your tennis game on well-maintained courts, or embark on leisurely hikes and bike rides along the scenic trails. Nature lovers and outdoor enthusiasts will find themselves in paradise, with Lake Tarpon just moments away for fishing and boating adventures. Don't miss this exceptional opportunity to live the resort-style life you've always dreamed of in the Deer Hollow community of Pine Ridge. Schedule a viewing today to discover the unparalleled charm and convenience this condo has to offer.
